  "title": "Flaming Arrow",
  "summaries": [
    "The <b>Flaming Arrow</b> is a type of <linked>arrow</linked>. It is an upgrade to the <linked>Wooden Arrow</linked>, dealing slightly more damage and having a chance to inflict the <linked>On Fire!</linked> <linked>debuff</linked> on <linked>enemies</linked>. It emits light when fired or dropped, making it useful for temporary lighting in a cave.",
    "If a Flaming Arrow gets in contact with <linked>water</linked>, <linked>honey</linked>, or <span class=\"eil\"><span><linked>shimmer</linked></span><span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span></span>, it will no longer emit light or inflict the On Fire! debuff. Its sprite also becomes identical to the Wooden Arrow's sprite.",
    "<span class=\"eico i3 i5\" title=\"Old-gen console and 3DS versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> Flaming Arrows have a chance to be recoverable after hitting a surface or a target. If they remained lit, they have a <span class=\"chance\"><s>11.11*</s>1/9 (11.11%)</span> chance to drop as Flaming Arrows and a <span class=\"chance\"><s>22.22*</s>2/9 (22.22%)</span> chance to drop as Wooden Arrows. Otherwise, they have a <span class=\"chance\"><s>33.33*</s>1/3 (33.33%)</span> chance to drop as Wooden Arrows."
  ],
